column3: â€œChunky Diesel is one of the best sativa-dominant hybrid strains in Illinois! I highly recommend Chu...â€

â€œNot sure why this is listed as strictly a Sativa and not a hybrid. Cresco labs brand of Chunky Diesel is the best Diesel I've ever smoked. â€œChunky Diesel - you make me want to do the truffle shuffle.  Cresco really knocked it out of the park with this one! â€œChunky Diesel produces a dense bud that fluffs up in volume when ground. A strong gasoline soaked dark-chocolate flavor is surprisingly pleasant. â€œMy new favorite Sativa strain, without a doubt! Has a great euphoric and happy feeling. The chocolatey smell is wonderful and still offers that nice diesel undertone that I love.  A great strain to medicate with if you plan to be in a social setting.â€

â€œI smoke a lot of strains and often don't buy a particular strain more than once. Chunky Diesel is in our regular rotation for hybrids. It's not my favorite, but it's a crowd pleaser for sure...
